{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a00971d631","title":"向董其武部调派的政工干部必须加以训练","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"017c4c53cd","index":0,"year":1949,"month":11,"day":11,"articleId":"a00971d631"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"7fa26f8af9","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"a00971d631","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东为中共中央军委总政治部起草的给华北军区司令员最荣臻、政治委员薄一波、政治部副主任张南生和张致祥的电报。"},{"id":"6787d1f67d","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"a00971d631","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"董其武，原任国民党绥远省政府主席、国民党军西北军政长官公署副长官，1949年9月率部在绥远起义。1949年10月任政协第一届全国委员会委员。"},{"id":"dc33989991","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"a00971d631","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"绥远，旧省名，辖今内蒙古自治区中部地区，1954年撤销。"}],"contents":[{"id":"eeaaefd0a1","type":"title","text":"向董其武部调派的政工干部必须加以训练","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"a00971d631"},{"id":"7fa26f8af9","type":"paragraph","text":"慧、薄、张、张：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"a00971d631"},{"id":"6787d1f67d","type":"paragraph","text":"成江电悉。同意所提调任改编董其武部两个军七个师之师以上政治干部配备全部名单。所有这些政治工作干部必须调集一起有计划地给以去绥远军队工作的方针政策和方法的训练，并完全研究明白，然后派去，否则不要派去，务望注意为要","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"a00971d631"},{"id":"dc33989991","type":"paragraph","text":"军委总政","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"a00971d631"},{"id":"d6638ac1b0","type":"paragraph","text":"成真","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"a00971d631"}],"page":{"id":"391b2ef6a8","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"a00971d631","start":508,"end":508}}}},"__N_SSG":true}